      <hedline>
        <hl1>EARTHLINK LOSS NARROWS</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Earthlink reports smaller-than-expected net loss for second quarter, as revenue rose by more than 40 percent; loss was $35.2 million compared with $50.9 million a year ago (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Internet service provider EarthLink reported a smaller-than-expected net loss for the second quarter yesterday, as revenue at the Atlanta-based company rose by more than 40 percent. EarthLink said its second-quarter loss, excluding special items, was $35.2 million, compared with $50.9 million a year earlier.</p>
        <p>(NYTimes.com/TheStreet.com)</p>
      </block>
